<section id="how_it_works" class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-800">
  <div class="mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-center text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-12 leading-tight">
      How Hadaa Ai Landscaper Works: <br class="hidden md:inline">Your Vision, Simplified
    </h2>

    <p class="text-center text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 text-neutral-700">
      Designing your dream garden has never been this intuitive or powerful. Hadaa Ai Landscaper guides you through a seamless process, turning your ideas into reality with just a few clicks and strokes.
    </p>

    <div data-controller="slider" class="relative">
      <button data-action="slider#prev" class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 cursor-pointer -translate-y-1/2 bg-neutral-700/70 hover:bg-neutral-500 text-text-light p-3 rounded-full z-20 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-200">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" />
        </svg>
      </button>
      <button data-action="slider#next" class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 cursor-pointer -translate-y-1/2 bg-neutral-700/70 hover:bg-neutral-500 text-text-light p-3 rounded-full z-20 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-neutral-900 transition-colors duration-200">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </button>

     <div data-slider-target="track" class="flex overflow-x-hidden scroll-smooth snap-x snap-mandatory gap-4 md:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/upload.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">1</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Upload Your Photo</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                Start by uploading a clear photo of your existing garden, backyard, patio, or any outdoor area you wish to transform. Hadaa uses this as the canvas for your <b>AI-powered design</b>, ensuring your new vision blends seamlessly with your current space.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center"  style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/brush_tool.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">2</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Brush Areas to Modify</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                This is where Hadaa truly stands out. Instead of just selecting styles, use our <b>intuitive brush tool</b> to directly draw on the areas you want to change or enhance. Want to add a new flower bed, reshape a lawn, or extend a patio? Simply brush over the area, and our AI will understand your intent, allowing for <b>precise, free-form modifications</b>.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center"  style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/zone.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">3</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Select Your Zone or Climate</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                Ensure your design <b>thrives year-round!</b> Choose your specific USDA plant hardiness zone or general climate type (e.g., arid, temperate, tropical). This crucial step allows Hadaa to provide <b>tailored plant recommendations</b> that are guaranteed to flourish in your unique environment, making your garden resilient for all four seasons.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center"  style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/style.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">4</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Select Your Location</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                For even greater accuracy and <b>hyper-localized plant suggestions</b>, simply input your specific location. Hadaa leverages this precise data to refine plant recommendations, ensuring they are perfectly suited to your local soil conditions, sunlight patterns, and microclimates.
                This is also used to generate your shopping list.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center"  style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/get_design.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">5</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Get Your Design</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                Watch as Hadaa's AI instantly transforms your brushed areas, climate preferences, and location data into a <b>stunning, photorealistic landscape design</b>. Explore a variety of garden styles like Zen, Desert, Cottage, and more. Experiment with different layouts and elements until you achieve your perfectly envisioned outdoor look.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center"  style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/shopping_list.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">6</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Generate Your Shopping List</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                Once your <b>AI-powered design</b> is finalized, Hadaa takes the guesswork out of procurement. It automatically generates a <b>comprehensive shopping list</b> of all the plants, hardscaping materials, and essential elements needed to bring your dream design to vivid reality. This feature saves you precious time and helps prevent costly purchasing mistakes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-full md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-2 snap-start flex flex-col">
          <div class="bg-neutral-800 text-text-light rounded-lg shadow-xl overflow-hidden transform transition duration-300  group flex-grow">
            <div class="relative h-80 lg:h-62 bg-cover bg-center"  style="background-image: url('<%= image_url('how_it_works/instructions.webp')%>');">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-neutral-900/60 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-accent group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">7</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3 text-text-secondary">Get Planting Instructions & Placement Ideas</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-neutral-300">
                Beyond just a list, Hadaa empowers you to succeed. We provide <b>detailed, easy-to-follow planting instructions</b> for each recommended plant, ensuring optimal growth. Plus, get <b>smart plant placement ideas</b> to arrange your flora and features optimally for aesthetics, light, and drainage, ensuring your garden looks its absolute best year-round.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<div class="flex mt-6 w-full justify-center">
     <%= render ButtonComponent.new(
        text: "Try now, free for life!",
      href: new_landscape_path,
      classes: "mt-4 inline-block bg-primary hover:bg-secondary text-text-light font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg transition duration-300 ease-in-out transform hover:scale-105"
      ) %>
</div>
</section>
